  <brief_title>Effect Of Preoperative Chemotherapy On Short-Term Outcome After Pancreatic Resection</brief_title>
  <official_title>PREOPERATIVE CHEMOTHERAPY DOES NOT ADVERSELY AFFECT SHORT-TERM OUTCOME AFTER PANCREATIC RESECTION.</official_title>
